title: Diamond V midlaner looking for a team
body:
Hi, i've just moved to OCE and i'd like to find a team (if possible plat+ but level is not that important) to try to play seriously but with a good mindset. I can also play as a jungle at the same level.

Add me in game if you're interested.

replies.body: Add me in game team consists of plats and gold's if interested
